# ============================================
# CONSTRUCTIVE VOTE OF NO CONFIDENCE (if reformed)
# ============================================

@constructive_vonc_attempt
title: Opposition Attempts Constructive Vote
subtitle: They're trying to replace us with a new government
new-page: true
view-if: constructive_vonc = 1 and spd_in_government = 1 and coalition_dissent >= 3
max-visits: 1
tags: event
on-arrival: {!
// Determine who is trying to form alternative government
if (Q.nsdap_r + Q.dnvp_r + Q.dvp_r >= 50) {
    Q.alternative_coalition = "right-wing";
    Q.alternative_chancellor = "Hitler";
} else if (Q.z_r + Q.dvp_r + Q.ddp_r >= 50) {
    Q.alternative_coalition = "bourgeois";
    Q.alternative_chancellor = "Brüning";
} else {
    Q.alternative_coalition = "none";
}
!}
go-to: constructive_vonc_right if alternative_coalition = "right-wing"; constructive_vonc_bourgeois if alternative_coalition = "bourgeois"; constructive_vonc_fails if alternative_coalition = "none"

@constructive_vonc_right

= Right-Wing Power Grab

**The NSDAP, DNVP, and DVP have united to replace our government!**

They've proposed Hitler as Chancellor with a right-wing coalition majority.

Under constructive vote of no confidence rules, they can only replace us if they have an alternative majority.

**Proposed Government:**
- NSDAP
- DNVP  
- DVP
- Total: ~[+ nsdap_r + dnvp_r + dvp_r +]%

This would mean Nazi power.

**Can we stop this?**

- @constructive_vonc_fight: Fight this with everything we have
- @constructive_vonc_accept_right: Accept democratic defeat

@constructive_vonc_bourgeois

= Bourgeois Coalition Alternative

**The Center Party and DVP propose replacing us with a bourgeois coalition.**

Brüning would become Chancellor of a government excluding the SPD.

**Proposed Government:**
- Center Party
- DVP
- [+ ddp_name +]

**What should we do?**

- @constructive_vonc_fight: Fight to maintain our government
- @constructive_vonc_accept_bourgeois: Step aside

@constructive_vonc_fails

= Constructive Vote Fails

The opposition has called a constructive vote of no confidence, but they cannot agree on an alternative government.

Our government survives by default!

The constitutional reform requiring a constructive vote has saved us.

@constructive_vonc_fight
choose-if: resources >= 4
unavailable-subtitle: Need 4 resources to mount effective resistance
on-arrival: resources -= 4; coalition_dissent -= 1
go-to: constructive_vonc_barely_survives if coalition_dissent < 3; constructive_vonc_fight_fails if coalition_dissent >= 3

@constructive_vonc_barely_survives

Through intense lobbying and political maneuvering, we've prevented the alternative coalition from forming!

Our government survives, but barely.

@constructive_vonc_fight_fails
on-arrival: spd_in_government = 0
go-to: constructive_vonc_right_succeeds if alternative_coalition = "right-wing"; constructive_vonc_bourgeois_succeeds if alternative_coalition = "bourgeois"

@constructive_vonc_right_succeeds
on-arrival: chancellor = "Hitler"; chancellor_party = "NSDAP"; pro_republic -= 20; coup_progress += 5

